      "name": "Mesh independence study — FDA centrifugal pump geometry",
      "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) analysis performed on three mesh densities (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M cells). GCI < 1.2% for shear-stress-derived hemolysis index at all five operating points. Discretization error confirmed acceptable at MRL 2 required level.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/mesh-independence-study-report-2024"
