    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error exceeds requirement (GCI 1.2% vs. 5% threshold). Experimental comparison demonstrates MAE of 8.3% within the 15% acceptance band. Worst-case operating point correctly identified. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model is deemed credible for the stated COU. Recommendation: accept simulation results in support of 510(k) regulatory submission.",
